 (\mathcal F (f''))(t) = \int_{-\infty}^\infty e^{-itx} \delta(x-5)\,dx = e^{-5it}. 
 (\mathcal F (f'))(t) = -it(\mathcal F f)(t), 
 (\mathcal F (f''))(t) = -t^2(\mathcal F f)(t). 
